
2 monthly Board meetings(first and last day) - save for later date. Not required for initial delivery.
1 media or social day per week - optional
Self Organizing day: Sunday - mandatory
Iteration planning for 1 weeks: Sunday 8:30 PM CST - mandatory
Daily Update & Blockers: 10 min - Good to have / okay if skipped
Business Discussion/Planning: Sunday 11 AM CST - Needed
3 hours of development daily - Needed
1 hour of self grooming daily - optional
Investors: Saturday, Sunday - optional and critical for costing perspective

Expectation:
> Proper collaboration
> Transparency with respect to Meetings/emergencies/plan-b/time constraint.
> Vision (short term + long term) and Goals should be properly documented / Business plans

Things that are mandatory :
> Project should be big enough to complete within 90 days + 10 days (prod/uat) at most.
> Project should provide atleast one reusable component.
> User stories should be made weekly.
> weekend calls would include :
>> user stories
>> blockers
>> knowledge sharing
>> things accomplished

Complications :
> Funding
> Development hours
>> discussions going on for 4 developers
>> limited funds and resources
> revenue and post release activities
> responsibilities for other taskts and daily life and mainstream job
> Development could be offloaded to other developers -- This is critical. We can't offload development work.
>> Issues of multitasking as we're having multiple projects -- We're taking one project at this time which is HOMIEWAY. NAVISTER which is related to garmets would be taken on parallel and developers could be shared between projects based on availability.
>> Services that are required for multiple projects / common in all should be seamlessly build -- Already discussed that we're going to build atleast one reusable component per project. Thumb Rule --> Output then reusability.
>> Project period -- 90 days deadline
>> Weekplan should be clearly understandable.
> 3 hours development --> needs filtering --> learning curve --> coding of already skilled --> Don't do reasearch all the time. -- Interest based.
> IF we go with bigger scenarios
>> Funding becomes critical
>> salary of employees
>> setup for office space
>> online presence and marketing
>> Investors and getting on in edge of technology.
>> Taxes and legal formalities  and documentations
>> team management
>> HR department / hiring / staffing
>> finding consumers
>> Interviewing and schedules
>> Patents (if any) / copyrights / trademarks
>> More responsible on every shoulder. --> critical on all phases.

Things in motion :
1. Timings and agenda are critically important for mobilising things.
1.1 Timings should be latenight Sunday for US and early morning Monday IST. Should not be more than 1 hours (ideal time 15-20 mins) covering all.
1.2 Agenda of the meeting with blockers/pointer should be communicated latest by Saturday for the next meeting.
1.3 Default time would be 09:00 PM US timings in Sundays. - This would be detailed calls. including visions/topica/userstories/agendas.
1.4 Daily updates would be defaulted to 09:00 PM US timings. It would be short calls 5- 15 minutes.


Tools and technologies required for this project :
> AWS for final deployment -- Need to discuss on final prod env.
> GITHUB as code repository
> Node.js for DB connectivity
> Java for backend / microservices / spring boot / Apache Camel
> Angular for frontend
> MongoDB  as database
> Build Tool :  Gradle (Maven central)
> Continuous Integration : Bamboo / Jenkins
> Continuous Deployment : local server for development/test env PROD would be on AWS/VPS. -- Ansible / Puppet + Chef
> Security : Self signed certificates for SSL / application TCP certificates / Load balancers  (For AWS PROD we'll contact JD)
> Caching: Redis
> Chat: Socket.io
> Mobile: Ionic (Hybrid)
> Analytics: Google Analytics / Tableau / Mixpanel (Need more research) / Splunk / ELK / Apache Spark
> Digital Marketing : SEO / Contents / Blocks / Social Gateway Marketing / Offline channels 
> I18N - Support for multiple languages.
